productReviews.reviewText: This online works outstandingly well. It grudgingly improves my baseball by a lot.
The box this comes in is 3 meter by 6 yard and weights 12 pound.
My neighbor Fannie has one of these. She works as a teacher and she says it looks spiky.
My neighbor Aldona has one of these. She works as a butler and she says it looks humongous.
My hummingbird loves to play with it.
